"yasya ca bhāvena bhāvalakṣaṇam" iti saptamī || madhye śyāmaḥ śeṣe madhyād anyatra vistāre paritaḥ pāṇḍur hariṇaḥ || "hariṇaḥ pāṇḍuraḥ pāṇḍuḥ" ity amaraḥ || bhuvaḥ stana iva | amaramithunānām | khecarāṇām iti bhāvaḥ | prekṣaṇīyāṃ darśanīyām avasthāṃ nūnaṃ yāsyati | mithunagrahaṇaṃ kāminām eva stanatvenotprekṣā sambhavatīti kṛtam | yathā pariśrāntaḥ kaścit kāmī kāminīnāṃ kucakalaśe viśrāntaḥ sansvapiti tadvad bhavān api bhuvo nāyikāyāḥ stana iti dhvaniḥ ||

<commentary>sthitveti || he megha, vane caranti te vanacarāḥ || tatpuruṣe kṛti bahulam" iti bahulagrahaṇād lug bhavati || teṣāṃ vadhūbhir muktāḥ kuñjā latāgṛhā yatra tasmin || nikuñjakuñjau vā klībe latādipihitodare ity amaraḥ || tatra te nayanavinodo 'stīty arthaḥ | tasmin āmrakūṭe muhūrtam alpakālam | na tu ciraṃ svakāryavirodhād iti bhāvaḥ || "muhūrtam alpakāle syād ghaṭikādvitaye 'pi ca" iti śabdārṇave || sthitvā viśramya | toyotsargeṇa "tvām āsāra-" ity uktavarṣeṇena drutataragatir lāghavād dhetor atikṣipragamanaḥ san | tasmād āmrakūṭāt param anantaraṃ tatparaṃ vartma mārgaṃ tīrṇo 'tikrāntaḥ | upalaiḥ pāṣāṇair viṣame vindhyasyādreḥ pāde prasyantaparvate || "pādāḥ pratyantaparvatāḥ" ity amaraḥ || viśīrṇāṃ samantato visṛmarām || etena kasyāścit kāmukyā priyatamacaraṇapāto 'pi dhvanyate || revāṃ narmadām || "revā tu narmadā somodbhavā mekhalakanyakā" ity amaraḥ || gajasyāṅge śarīre bhaktayo racanāḥ | revā iti yāvat || "bhaktir niṣevaṇe bhāge racanāyām" iti śabdārṇave || tāsāṃ chedair bhaṅgibhir bhābhir viracitāṃ bhūtiṃ śṛṅgāram iva bhasitam iva vā || "bhūtir mātaṅgaśṛṅgāre jātau bhasmani saṃpadi" iti viśvaḥ || drakṣyasi | ayam api mahāṃs te nayana kautukalābha iti bhāvaḥ ||</commentary>

tasyā iti || he megha vāntavṛṣṭir udgīrṇavarṣaḥ san |
